        "content": "\n**Untested:** `_line`, `notify_console`, `notify_slack`, `notify_webhook`, `notify_email`, `_sms_body`, `notify_sms`, `dispatch`.\n\n**Gaps:**\n- Every notifier's **env-var gate**: missing var(s) → silent no-op, no network call\n- Every notifier's **empty new/changed gate**: configured but nothing to send → no-op\n- `notify_sms`/`notify_slack`/`notify_webhook`: actual payload shape sent (mock `httpx.post`)\n- `notify_sms.raise_for_status()` on Twilio failure — is this caught by `dispatch`'s try/except? (yes, but untested)\n- **`dispatch` error isolation** — the most important integration-style gap: one notifier raising must not block the others.\n- `_sms_body` truncation at `limit` (`+N more` line)\n\n```python\n",
